metadata.name: Lips 1
metadata.description:
Hello friends.
Here is pic 1 which I will mail to whoever buys it first.
This collection is about a glow-in-the-dark picture I made with fluorescent paints (glows under ultraviolet light).
There are 10 pictures.
As the title suggests, it's about lips that shine out of the dark.
What do you think of when you think of lips?
Look at the picture and follow your own associations.
Yours, Sebastian Becker Weimar (NFT-Beckus86-NFT)
